## üéØ KEY FEATURES BY CATEGORY

### AI-Powered Features (Must Have)
- **24/7 AI Tutor** - Doubt solving, concept explanations
- **Adaptive Practice Sessions** - Personalized tests based on weak areas
- **Performance Predictions** - Exam score forecasts
- **Learning Pattern Analysis** - Study habits, effectiveness
- **Smart Note-Taking** - Auto-generated notes from lectures
- **Concept Mapping** - AI-generated mind maps
- **Progress Prediction** - Success probability tracking
- **Weak Topic Detection** - ML-based gap identification
- **Motivational Coaching** - Psychology-based encouragement
- **Study Schedule Optimizer** - AI-created timetables

### Automated Communication Features (Must Have)
- **Automated Progress Reports** - Weekly/monthly AI-generated
- **Predictive Alerts** - Early warning system
- **Smart Notification System** - Optimal timing
- **WhatsApp Integration** - Automated messages
- **Voice Message Summaries** - Audio feedback conversion
- **Multi-channel Delivery** - SMS, Email, Push, WhatsApp

### Performance Tracking Features (Must Have)
- **Real-time Performance Tracking** - All subjects
- **Learning Gap Analysis** - Knowledge gaps identification
- **Attention Pattern Recognition** - Engagement tracking
- **Predictive Performance Modeling** - Forecasts with interventions
- **Comparison Analytics** - Benchmarking vs peers
- **Achievement Recognition** - Badges, milestones

### Financial Features (Must Have)
- **Smart Fee Reminders** - Graduated sequences
- **Payment Prediction** - Delay forecasting
- **Dynamic Pricing Display** - Market-based fee info
- **Scholarship Recommendations** - AI-identified eligibility
- **Payment Analytics** - Spending patterns

